, "text": "LL", "words": [163]}, {"id": 51, "text": "b.", "words": [164]}, {"id": 52, "text": "Enchanté, madame!", "words": [165, 166]}, {"id": 53, "text": ".", "words": [167]}, {"id": 54, "text": "Notre mariage est le 1* août.", "words": [168, 169, 170, 171, 172, 173]}, {"id": 55, "text": "a.", "words": [174]}, {"id": 56, "text": "Toutes mes félicitations !", "words": [175, 176, 177, 178]}, {"id": 57, "text": "b.", "words": [179]}, {"id": 58, "text": "Je vous en prie !", "words": [180, 181, 182, 183, 184]}, {"id": 59, "text": "2.", "words": [185]}, {"id": 60, "text": "Je vais me marier le mois prochain !", "words": [186, 187, 188, 189, 190, 191, 192, 193]}, {"id": 61, "text": "3.", "words": [194]}, {"id": 62, "text": "J'ai eu un petit accident de voiture !", "words": [195, 196, 197, 198, 199, 200, 201, 202]}, {"id": 63, "text": "4.", "words": [203]}, {"id": 64, "text": "La semaine dernière, j'ai eu une promotion !", "words": [204, 205, 206, 207, 208, 209, 210, 211]}, {"id": 65, "text": "5, Vous savez, j'ai perdu ma femme le mois dernier !", "words": [212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 217, 218, 219, 220, 221, 222]}, {"id": 66, "text": "6.", "words": [223]}, {"id": 67, "text": "Maman, j'ai gagné le match de tennis !", "words": [224, 225, 226, 227, 228, 229, 230, 231]}, {"id": 68, "text": "| 4 2 Trouvez une réponse possible.", "words": [232, 233, 234, 235, 236, 237, 238]}, {"id": 69, "text": "1.", "words": [239]}, {"id": 70, "text": "Bonjour, Kevin, comment vas-tu ?", "words": [240, 241, 242, 243, 244]}, {"id": 71, "text": "2.", "words": [245]}, {"id": 72, "text": "Je vous remercie !", "words": [246, 247, 248, 249]}, {"id": 73, "text": "3.", "words": [250]}, {"id": 74, "text": "Vous pouvez me passer le pain, s'il vous plaît ?", "words": [251, 252, 253, 254, 255, 256, 257, 258, 259, 260]}, {"id": 75, "text": "4.", "words": [261]}, {"id": 76, "text": "Nous allons nous marier !", "words": [262, 263, 264, 265, 266]}, {"id": 77, "text": "5.", "words": [267]}, {"id": 78, "text": "Je